			</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Von <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/thejunzhangrw\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a019a40d289ee27b558ac32584be44a6?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a019a40d289ee27b558ac32584be44a6?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/thejunzhangrw\" class=\"reviewer-name\">thejunzhangrw</a> am <span class=\"review-date\">April 17, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Good plugin and works like a charm.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Clumsy and unsophisticated</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 von 5 Sternen\" data-title-template=\"%s von 5 Sternen\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Von <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/susantfl\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/541ae2f8c2a3c823107824a21ce0927c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/541ae2f8c2a3c823107824a21ce0927c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/susantfl\" class=\"reviewer-name\">susantfl</a> am <span class=\"review-date\">April 16, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Like so many Wordpress plugins, you would think this had been written about 20 years ago.  All the shop items have to be created as a wordpress page. I deleted it soon after installing, when I realised how bad it was.  But the worst thing was that several hours later I realised it had changed my default home page to its ugly shop page, which was still there even though the plugin was gone.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">4.0 update images missing</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 von 5 Sternen\" data-title-template=\"%s von 5 Sternen\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Von <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kjrichey\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/cbb474086bbe42019c94affcc92f7c24?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/cbb474086bbe42019c94affcc92f7c24?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kjrichey\" class=\"reviewer-name\">kjrichey</a> am <span class=\"review-date\">April 13, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I am PISSED off I have a highly trafficked store and with this last update my images are not showing up on my products. I donât want this I need the precious version or this to be fixed ASAP I wasnât have any problem with anything until this update.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Horrible and slow new dashboard</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 von 5 Sternen\" data-title-template=\"%s von 5 Sternen\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Von <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/lifeforceinst\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/96ddeb71608e01d6b57d3b0e441a39e1?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/96ddeb71608e01d6b57d3b0e441a39e1?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/lifeforceinst\" class=\"reviewer-name\">lifeforceinst</a> am <span class=\"review-date\">April 13, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Like so many others have mentioned this new dashboard with WC 4.0 is horrible bloatware and takes heaps of unnecessary resources.\n\nIt is appallingly slow takes ages to load, is full of bugs where some items do not load, seems to uses heaps of REST API calls and java to load data into the blank tables. For the majority of shop managers and site admins this produces no additional benefits, instead it makes duplicate tables in the database is also a total waste of system resources.\n\nThis should not and never have been made part of the WC core, it would be provided as an optional plugin which those who want it can optionally load.\n\nIt would have been much better us of resources if Automatic had focused on addressing many of the systemic database issues (such as separating orders, products and such out from the posts table) rather than introducing this bloatware.\n\nI am advising every client not to go near WC4.0, until this bloatware is removed.  I do know many who are starting to look at alternatives as well.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Perfect shop</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 von 5 Sternen\" data-title-template=\"%s von 5 Sternen\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Von <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bulletrainy\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/eedae12fba4ab85b750c0e889864db30?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/eedae12fba4ab85b750c0e889864db30?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bulletrainy\" class=\"reviewer-name\">bulletrainy</a> am <span class=\"review-date\">April 11, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This is really perfect shop. So flexible with high performance. Thanks!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Excellent for a (very) small business</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 von 5 Sternen\" data-title-template=\"%s von 5 Sternen\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Von <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/murdersbymail\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/05d5963f548cf74023e337ea40ca67dd?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/05d5963f548cf74023e337ea40ca67dd?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/murdersbymail\" class=\"reviewer-name\">murdersbymail</a> am <span class=\"review-date\">April 6, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Super-happy with Woocommerce for our very small store. Was up and selling products in a day! We\'ll be growing our products slowly, but have no doubt Woo will continue to be a great tool.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Some things missing, but...</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 von 5 Sternen\" data-title-template=\"%s von 5 Sternen\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Von <a href=\"https://profil