ion/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">UpiCRM</a> is a useful standalone tool. Using UpiCRM makes it easy to manage, track, collect and protect your sales leads.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\n</div><ul class=\"fusion-checklist fusion-checklist-7\" style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:27.2px;\"><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-arrow-alt-circle-right far\" style=\"color:#65bc7b;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">Aggregate your leads from multiple sites.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-arrow-alt-circle-right far\" style=\"color:#65bc7b;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">Assign leads to specific sales representatives with ease.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-arrow-alt-circle-right far\" style=\"color:#65bc7b;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">The automated lead management process is easy to configure to your needs.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-arrow-alt-circle-right far\" style=\"color:#65bc7b;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">Advanced analytics, monitoring, and tracking to help measure the effectiveness of your marketing and sales efforts.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-arrow-alt-circle-right far\" style=\"color:#65bc7b;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">Straightforward, interactive dashboards that offer the ability to track key performance indicators.</div></li></ul><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:30px;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-8 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"font-size:32px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;\" id=\"wpsystem\"><h3 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;font-size:1em;\"><a style=\"color: #292a2c; hover: #65bc7b;\" href=\"https://www.wp-crm.com/\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">WP-CRM System</a></h3></div><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\" class=\"fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-7\"><a class=\"fusion-no-lightbox\" href=\"https://en-gb.wordpress.org/plugins/wp-crm-system/\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"WP-CRM Systen\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/wpcrmsystem-compressor.png\" data-orig-src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/wpcrmsystem-compressor.png\" width=\"1544\" height=\"500\" alt=\"WP-CRM System\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-728851\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271544%27%20height%3D%27500%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201544%20500%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271544%27%20height%3D%273500%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/wpcrmsystem-compressor-200x65.png 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/wpcrmsystem-compressor-400x130.png 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/wpcrmsystem-compressor-600x194.png 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/wpcrmsystem-compressor-800x259.png 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/wpcrmsystem-compressor-1200x389.png 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/wpcrmsystem-compressor.png 1544w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:20px;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>Not to be confused with the WP-CRM mentioned above, <a href=\"https://en-gb.wordpress.org/plugins/wp-crm-system/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">WP-CRM System</a> is a lightweight CRM that integrates directly with your WordPress dashboard. Developers love it as it&#8217;s easy to customize for your individual needs.</p>\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\n</div><ul class=\"fusion-checklist fusion-checklist-8\" style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:27.2px;\"><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-arrow-alt-circle-right far\" style=\"color:#65bc7b;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">Manage detailed client information with custom fields.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-arrow-alt-circle-right far\" style=\"color:#65bc7b;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">Integration with popular third-party tools like Zendesk, Mailchimp, Slack, and Gravity Forms.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-arrow-alt-circle-right far\" style=\"color:#65bc7b;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">The plugin includes a built-in invoicing system that integrates with Stripe.</div></li></ul><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:30px;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-9 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"font-size:32px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;\" id=\"ukuupeople\"><h3 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;font-size:1em;\"><a style=\"color: #292a2c; hover: #65bc7b;\" href=\"https://ukuupeople.com/\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Ukuupeople</a></h3></div><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\" class=\"fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-8\"><a class=\"fusion-no-lightbox\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/ukuupeople-the-simple-crm/\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"UkuuPeople CRM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ukuupeople-compressor.png\" data-orig-src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ukuupeople-compressor.png\" width=\"1544\" height=\"500\" alt=\"UkuuPeople CRM\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-728856\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271544%27%20height%3D%27500%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201544%20500%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271544%27%20height%3D%273500%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ukuupeople-compressor-200x65.png 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ukuupeople-compressor-400x130.png 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ukuupeople-compressor-600x194.png 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ukuupeople-compressor-800x259.png 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ukuupeople-compressor-1200x389.png 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ukuupeople-compressor.png 1544w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:20px;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/ukuupeople-the-simple-crm/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Ukuupeople</a> offers a super simple CRM for organizing your contacts. It provides an easy way to combine all of the WordPress tools you are already using, including Gravity Forms and Google products, into a streamlined database for your contacts. With a simplified interface within WordPress, you can easily store your contacts&#8217; information and track your team members&#8217; interactions with all of your contacts.</p>\n<p><strong>Key features:</strong></p>\n</div><ul class=\"fusion-checklist fusion-checklist-9\" style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:27.2px;\"><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-arrow-alt-circle-right far\" style=\"color:#65bc7b;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">Track touchpoints, aka interactions, with contacts.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-arrow-alt-circle-right far\" style=\"color:#65bc7b;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">Track potential, in progress, and won opportunities to help drive more sales.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-arrow-alt-circle-right far\" style=\"color:#65bc7b;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">The option of many add-on features, including syncing with Google Calendar and Gravity Forms.</div></li></ul><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:30px;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-10 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"font-size:32px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;\" id=\"wperp\"><h3 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;font-size:1em;\"><a style=\"color: #292a2c; hover: #65bc7b;\" href=\"https://wperp.com/\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">WP ERP</a></h3></div><div class=\"imageframe-liftup\"><span style=\"border:1px solid #e0dede;\" class=\"fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-9\"><a class=\"fusion-no-lightbox\" href=\"https://en-gb.wordpress.org/plugins/erp/\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"WP ERP\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/weberp-compressor.png\" data-orig-src=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/weberp-compressor.png\" width=\"1544\" height=\"500\" alt=\"WP ERP\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-728858\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271544%27%20height%3D%27500%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201544%20500%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271544%27%20height%3D%273500%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/weberp-compressor-200x65.png 200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/weberp-compressor-400x130.png 400w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/weberp-compressor-600x194.png 600w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/weberp-compressor-800x259.png 800w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/weberp-compressor-1200x389.png 1200w, https://theme-fusion.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/weberp-compressor.png 1544w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a></span></div><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:20px;\"></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p><a href=\"https://en-gb.wordpress.org/plugins/erp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">WP ERP</a> is an open-source WordPress CRM that gives you the ability to track your leads, follow up with contacts, and develop valuable relationships for your company. There is also a dashboard where you can view your calendar for the day and an overview of contacts in your database.</p>\n<p><strong>Key features:</strong></p>\n</div><ul class=\"fusion-checklist fusion-checklist-10\" style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:27.2px;\"><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-arrow-alt-circle-right far\" style=\"color:#65bc7b;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">Add notes to your contact records to track essential details from your interactions.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-arrow-alt-circle-right far\" style=\"color:#65bc7b;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">Schedule meetings and follow-up tasks.</div></li><li class=\"fusion-li-item\"><span style=\"height:27.2px;width:27.2px;margin-right:11.2px;\" class=\"icon-wrapper circle-no\"><i class=\"fusion-li-icon fa-arrow-alt-circle-right far\" style=\"color:#65bc7b;\"></i></span><div class=\"fusion-li-item-content\" style=\"margin-left:38.4px;\">A built-in email system, so you don&#8217;t have to switch tools to email your contacts.</div></li></ul><div class=\"fusion-sep-clear\"></div><div class=\"fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-none\" style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;margin-bottom:30px;\"></div><style type=\"text/css\"></style><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-11 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;\"><h2 class=\"title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">Final Thoughts: Choosing the Best WordPress CRM Plugin for You</h2></div><div class=\"fusion-text\"><p>With the growing importance of CRMs for small and medium-sized businesses, dozens of new solutions are popping up to fill niche demands. Many of these solutions were created by people frustrated with the larger, clunkier systems they were using in their businesses.<br />\nChoosing the right CRM system for your team is crucial.</p>\n<p>According to <a href=\"https://hbr.org/2002/02/avoid-the-four-perils-of-crm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Gartner Group</a>, 55% of all CRM projects don&#8217;t produce results. However, it&#8217;s not a failure of the systems. Harvard Business Review has suggested these projects crash and burn because most executives don&#8217;t completely understand what they are implementing.</a></p>\n<p>The key is to find a CRM WordPress add-on that is easy to use so that your team won&#8217;t fall into old habits. After all, your CRM&#8217;s reports are only as good as the data provided. You also need a system that is powerful enough to give you new insights into your business&#8217;s performance. This will give you the freedom to adjust your sales and marketing tactics to meet your customers&#8217; needs better.</p>\n<p>Before you implement any WordPress CRM system (even a free one), make sure you have a clear idea of how it will align with your business&#8217;s process to increase customer loyalty and profits â this is what CRMs are all about.</p>\n<p>Tell us why you&#8217;re ready to start using a WordPress CRM plugin in the comments!</p>\n</div><div class=\"fusion-clearfix\"></div></div></div></div></div><style type=\"text/css\">.fusion-fullwidth.fusion-builder-row-1 a:not(.fusion-button):not(.fusion-builder-module-control):not(.fusion-social-network-icon):not(.fb-icon-element):not(.fusion-countdown-link):not(.fusion-rollover-link):not(.fusion-rollover-gallery):not(.fusion-button-bar):not(.add_to_cart_button):not(.show_details_button):not(.product_type_external):not(.fusion-quick-view):not(.fusion-rollover-title-link):not(.fusion-breadcrumb-link) , .fusion-fullwidth.fusion-builder-row-1 a:not(.fusion-button):not(.fusion-builder-module-control):not(.fusion-social-network-icon):not(.fb-icon-element):not(.fusion-countdown-link):not(.fusion-rollover-link):not(.fusion-rollover-gallery):not(.fusion-button-bar):not(.add_to_cart_button):not(.show_details_button):not(.product_type_external):not(.fusion-quick-view):not(.fusion-rollover-title-link):not(.fusion-breadcrumb-link):before, .fusion-fullwidth.fusion-builder-row-1 a:not(.fusion-button):not(.fusion-builder-module-control):not(.fusion-social-network-icon):not(.fb-icon-element):not(.fusion-countdown-link):not(.fusion-rollover-link):not(.fusion-rollover-gallery):not(.fusion-button-bar):not(.add_to_cart_button):not(.show_details_button):not(.product_type_external):not(.fusion-quick-view):not(.fusion-rollover-title-link):not(.fusion-breadcrumb-link):after {color: #111111;}.fusion-fullwidth.fusion-builder-row-1 a:not(.fusion-button):not(.fusion-builder-module-control):not(.fusion-social-network-icon):not(.fb-icon-element):not(.fusion-countdown-link):not(.fusion-rollover-link):not(.fusion-rollover-gallery):not(.fusion-button-bar):not(.add_to_cart_button):not(.show_details_button):not(.product_type_external